<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Hatak eho moyuma kʋt ƲIT119</title>
<time_sig>L.M. (8.8.8.8.)</time_sig>
<aka>Judgment: &quot;So then every one of us shall give account of himself to God.&quot;</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Hatak eho moyuma kʋt
 Nitak ishtaiyopi yoka
 Iloh anukfihinlashke;
 Palʋmmi fehna hi oke.

[V2]
 Isht si ahalaia keyu,
 Kiloh acho puyullashke;
 Enchel, hatak, micha Satan
 Moma nan im ʋlhpisa he.

[V3]
 Klaist Chisʋs itikba yʋno
 Hatak e moyuma hokʋt
 E hiela he mak oke;
 Il i̱ luma he keyushke.

[V4]
 Hatak e moyuma hoka
 Pi atokoli fehna he,
 Holisso holitopa ʋt
 Pim anoli chatuk oke.

[V5]
 Yʋmohmi ka, katiohmit
 Chihowa itikba yoka,
 Pi okcha̱ya ta̱kla kʋto
 E hiela he tuk oh cho?

[V6]
 Ʋba Pi̱ki pulla hoka
 Achukmʋlit im antiʋt,
 Il aha̱shwa hulla tuk osh,
 Aiachukma il onashke.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>119</hymn_number>
</song>